{"TopicId":160996,"ForumId":18,"TopicTitle":"Want a free space game?","CreatedByName":"Streetwind","CreatedById":98962,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-24T16:19:26Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Streetwind","CreatedById":98962,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-24T16:19:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0027Cause this is how you get a free space game:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStarpoint Gemini 2 and one of its DLCs is currently 100% off on Steam. I think the promotion expires really soon, like in an hour or so? I only learned about it myself just now through a friend.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGo get it while it\u0027s hot \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Shpaget","CreatedById":45577,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-24T17:11:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve never even heard about the game, or the developers, which I\u0027m kind of embarrass to admit considering the fact that I, apparently, pass by their headquarters twice every day.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NSEP","CreatedById":165635,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-24T18:03:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWoow! Awesome gottapropablycheckitout\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"StrandedonEarth","CreatedById":89439,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-24T22:36:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHmm, it said the free offer ended today at 10am Pacific time, but I just snagged it for free when I got home at 3:30 PT\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"qzgy","CreatedById":160994,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-25T00:32:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n8pm Eastern time - Still free!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Just Jim","CreatedById":148725,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-25T00:36:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo you mean the game FreeSpace? Or a free \u0022outer space\u0022 game?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-05-25T00:36:51Z\u0022 title=\u002205/25/2017 12:36  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EMay 25, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Just Jim\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"0111narwhalz","CreatedById":110660,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-25T00:41:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223066753\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022160996\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221495672571\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022148725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Just Jim\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 minutes ago, Just Jim said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo you mean the game FreeSpace? Or a free \u0022outer space\u0022 game?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI get the sense it\u0027s the latter.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Just Jim","CreatedById":148725,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-25T00:42:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223066757\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022160996\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221495672906\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022110660\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u00220111narwhalz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, 0111narwhalz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI get the sense it\u0027s the latter.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah... too bad, I\u0027d love a free\u00A0copy of FreeSpace... that was a great game!!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-05-25T00:42:59Z\u0022 title=\u002205/25/2017 12:42  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EMay 25, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Just Jim\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KerbMav","CreatedById":70338,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-25T11:58:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n... ... ...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt is fascinating - they seem to have a business adavantage from giving away free stuff. But for the last x times anyone gave something away for free, I only heard about it after is was over.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"pxi","CreatedById":78711,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-27T15:58:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223066289\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022160996\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221495642766\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002298962\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Streetwind\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 24/5/2017 at 5:19 PM, Streetwind said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStarpoint Gemini 2 and one of its DLCs is currently 100% off on Steam.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDidn\u0027t spot the free DLC at the time but went back and had a look at the DLC section for the game, and the free DLC is still available - seems to be the campaign for the original game remade in the new engine so essentially if you took them up on the offer you got two games for free.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223067099\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022160996\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221495713495\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002270338\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022KerbMav\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 25/5/2017 at 0:58 PM, KerbMav said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n... ... ...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt is fascinating - they seem to have a business adavantage from giving away free stuff. But for the last x times anyone gave something away for free, I only heard about it after is was over.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell they did release the next entry in the series 5 days ago, so essentially I\u0027d assume they\u0027re hoping the giveaway will act somewhat like a demo and entice you to buy the latest one.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFWIW I generally keep a reasonably close eye on the pcgamer website - their news section does a pretty good job of highlighting giveaways on steam/gog/humble bundle.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}